channel.title: Problem with ALL rsps CLIENTS
channel.description:

Heres my problem:
Now although it may sound "noobish", i cannot log into any client.
Whenever i try and log in, it doesn't even say "Connecting..." it just goes straight to the "Error Connecting" message
I am 99.9999% sure its not my firewall, and there are no other things that i can see that would affect this
ANY HELP WOULD BE APPRECIATED!
Thanks :/
~wcd727~
